      <title>中国科技、特斯拉飙升、比特币停滞 | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-25/bloomberg-technology-11-25-2024-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 分析了苹果首席执行官蒂姆·库克访华的意义。此外，还分析了特斯拉在选举后股价飙升的原因，以及比特币涨势在接近 10 万美元后停滞的原因。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-25/bloomberg-technology-11-25-2024-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 22:17:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zoom 公布符合预期的销售预测，投资者寻求更多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/zoom-projects-in-line-sales-forecast-while-investors-seek-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Zoom Video Communications Inc. 公布的本季度销售预测未能给那些期待该公司扩大产品套件将带来更大提振的投资者留下深刻印象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/zoom-projects-in-line-sales-forecast-while-investors-seek-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 21:35:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
